WEBVTT

00:01.814 --> 00:03.995
..learn about relationships
is that you're never done

00:04.005 --> 00:05.382
getting to know someone.

00:05.392 --> 00:07.133
Everyone has secrets.

00:07.143 --> 00:08.423
Some are nice.

00:08.433 --> 00:10.581
You know how to make crepes?

00:11.399 --> 00:13.072
That is so cool.

00:14.813 --> 00:16.675
