and counting you,

00:19.070 --> 00:21.943
- that puts the total up to--
- Oh, I got your total.

00:22.407 --> 00:23.830
I've been counting along.

00:25.123 --> 00:27.631
And some are just weird.

00:27.647 --> 00:30.133
You're scared of
the seven dwarfs?

00:30.149 --> 00:31.782
Just Doc. He's creepy.

00:31.799 --> 00:33.650
I mean the guy went
to medical school.

00:33.666 --> 00:36.070
What's he doing living
with six coal miners?

00:36.286 --> 00:38.753
Oh, man! I'm so excited.
I couldn't sleep last night.

00:38.766 --> 00:40.672
- I bet you guys couldn't either.
- Why?

00:40.688 --> 00:42.631
Only the Gala event
for the Grand Opening

00:42.648 --> 00:45.493
of Sharper Image's 500th store.
Didn't you get my email?

00:45.508 --> 00:48.001
No, I blocked your address
after the fourth time

00:48.015 --> 00:51.450
you sent me the video of the
monkey sniffing his own butt.

00:51.468 --> 00:53.971
Come on! It's on me.
I'm buying three of you foot massagers

00:53.987 --> 00:56.570
and one of you a nose hair trimmer.
You know who you are.

00:56.887 --> 00:58.030
Come on, let's go.

00:58.046 --> 00:59.011
Okay, I'm in.

00:59.027 --> 01:01.320
- To the Willowbrook Mall!
- To the Willowbrook Mall.

01:01.335 --> 01:04.272
Oh, it's at a mall?
I'm not going.

01:04.288 --> 01:05.521
What? Why not?

01:05.538 --> 01:07.633
I just don't feel
like going to a mall.

01:07.645 --> 01:09.563
We can split a Cinnabon.

01:09.578 --> 01:11.370
No, I'm really not going to go.

01:11.388 --> 01:14.273
- Come on, it'll be fun.
- No, I don't go to malls!

01:15.816 --> 01:18.600
Sorry, I just don't like malls.

01:18.617 --> 01:20.242
Why not?

01:20.776 --> 01:22.672
I'd rather not say.

01:23.006 --> 01:24.821
- Sharper Images.
- But that's where clothes live.

01:24.855 --> 01:26.922
Guys, guys, guys,
Robin doesn't like malls.

01:26.936 --> 01:29.320
If she doesn't want to tell us why,
she doesn't have to.

01:29.337 --> 01:31.673
I think we should all
just respect her privacy.

01:31.875 --> 01:33.103
Thanks, Ted.

01:33.115 --> 01:35.353
So, what's the deal
with you and malls?

01:35.366 --> 01:37.163
I thought you said that,
if I didn't want to talk about it,

01:37.198 --> 01:38.310
I didn't have to.

01:38.326 --> 01:40.050
Yeah, with those people.

01:40.067 --> 01:41.940
But I'm your boyfriend.
Come on. What is it?

01:41.955 --> 01:43.052
Did you get arrested at a mall?

01:43.087 --> 01:43.702
No.

01:43.717 --> 01:45.520
- Dumped at a mall?
- Ted.

01:45.538 --> 01:47.632
Found out you were
Canadian at a mall?

01:47.645 --> 01:48.613
Let it go.

01:48.627 --> 01:50.321
Trapped under a fake
boulder at a mall?

01:50.335 --> 01:52.600
- Let it go.
- Mauled at the mall?

01:52.617 --> 01:54.001
Let it go!

01:54.896 --> 01:58.120
And who gets trapped under
a fake boulder at the mall?

01:59.095 --> 02:02.720
Not me in Ohio when I was nine,
that's for sure.

