Robin has a secret.

02:24.847 --> 02:26.202
The more you learn
about a person,

02:26.217 --> 02:29.463
the better chance you have of
hitting the fatal "Oh" moment.

02:29.477 --> 02:30.590
The "Oh" moment?

02:30.608 --> 02:34.363
Yeah, that moment when you find
out that one detail about a person

02:34.378 --> 02:36.471
that is going to
be a deal breaker.

02:36.485 --> 02:38.122
It's a promise ring.

02:38.135 --> 02:41.651
I made a pact with God to stay
a virgin till I'm married.

02:44.008 --> 02:45.883
I don't have an
eating disorder.

02:45.898 --> 02:50.043
It's just when I put food in my mouth,
I chew it, and then I spit it out.

02:52.105 --> 02:53.550
I just turned 30.

02:55.868 --> 02:58.441
So trust me,
you want to postpone

02:58.458 --> 03:01.322
knowing anything about each
other for as long as possible.

03:01.338 --> 03:04.330
Mmm. I disagree.
If there is some potential "Oh" moment,

03:04.347 --> 03:07.150
I want to know about it right away.
I mean, what's the alternative?

03:07.226 --> 03:10.643
I now pronounce you,
man and wife.

03:12.995 --> 03:14.353
I love you.

03:14.388 --> 03:16.522
I used to be a dude.

03:18.238 --> 03:19.862
Yeah, I agree with Ted.

03:19.875 --> 03:22.821
In a real relationship,
you share everything.

03:22.838 --> 03:25.321
That's why Marshall and
I don't keep any secrets.

03:25.336 --> 03:27.721
You are such a cutie pie.
Here's a quarter.

03:27.735 --> 03:29.600
Go  play a song on the jukebox.

03:29.658 --> 03:31.882
No, it's true.
They tell each other everything.

03:31.897 --> 03:34.820
I can think of tons of things,
there's no way Marshall's told you.

03:34.835 --> 03:36.043
Try me.

03:37.608 --> 03:39.371
Do you know about the time
Marshall was in Trenton?

03:39.407 --> 03:41.051
Donkey ate his pants. Yup.

03:41.068 --> 03:42.662
Bill's bachelor
party in Memphis?

03:42.676 --> 03:45.620
Oh, when they had to pump out
all the nickels from his stomach?

03:45.638 --> 03:47.710
Wow. Okay. Seattle.

03:47.725 --> 03:50.553
Trick question. Marshall's never
been to the Pacific Northwest

03:50.566 --> 03:52.682
because he's afraid
of Sasquatch.

03:52.696 --> 03:53.952
Damn, you're good.

03:53.965 --> 03:57.502
I'm not afraid of Sasquatch,
I just think we should all be on alert.

03:58.217 --> 04:01.240
Trust me. Not only do they
tell each other everything,

04:01.256 --> 04:03.410
they want to know everything.

04:03.428 --> 04:05.630
So after the shower I was brushing
my teeth. And I was like,

04:05.668 --> 04:07.542
"Oh, man!
I wanted to have some orange juice.

04:07.557 --> 04:08.880
I should have done that first."

04:08.895 --> 04:10.550
But I already had the
toothpaste on the toothbrush.

04:10.586 --> 04:13.061
So I just went ahead
and brushed them anyway.

04:13.076 --> 04:15.220
What happened next?

04:17.346 --> 04:20.029
Yeah, meanwhile,
Robin tells me nothing.

04:20.075 --> 04:22.782
Fine. Do you want to know
what Robin's secret is?

04:22.797 --> 04:23.870
You know?

04:23.888 --> 04:25.342
Of course I know.

04:25.355 --> 04:27.271
She couldn't look at us,
her face got flushed--

04:27.287 --> 04:28.923
that's shame, my friend.

04:28.938 --> 04:33.720
Our friend Robin used to do porn,
wait for it...

04:33.827 --> 04:35.780
...ography.

04:35.878 --> 04:38.450
Yeah, we didn't really
need to wait for that.

04:38.468 --> 04:40.182
And it's ridiculous.

04:40.198 --> 04:41.702
I don't know.
He could be right.

04:41.718 --> 04:44.402
She does have the fake
orgasm noises down.

04:44.416 --> 04:45.193
Hey!

04:45.207 --> 04:46.802
What? The walls are thin.

04:46.815 --> 04:49.491
That's not what I'm
"hey"ing you about.

04:50.005 --> 04:51.502
You know what it might be?

04:51.515 --> 04:55.451
This is going to sound a little
crazy but what if Robin is married?

04:55.467 --> 04:58.101
Married? What does that
have to do with the mall?

04:58.118 --> 05:00.790
Well, maybe she got
married at the mall.

05:00.805 --> 05:02.492
Back home in Minnesota,
a ton of people get married

05:02.526 --> 05:04.560
at the Mall of America.
It's great.

05:04.578 --> 05:07.281
There's this gorgeous indoor 
golf course for pictures,

05:07.296 --> 05:09.790
numerous fine dining options,
and talk about a reasonable--

05:09.807 --> 05:12.853
- We are not getting married at the mall!
- Well, just meet with the guy.

05:12.925 --> 05:15.520
She's not married.
Robin hates marriage.

05:15.535 --> 05:17.952
Because she already
got married.

05:17.966 --> 05:19.681
At the mall.

05:19.695 --> 05:22.850
No,  because before Robin
moved to New York, she...

05:23.328 --> 05:24.820
What was she doing?

05:24.878 --> 05:27.002
Well, I don't know.
Whenever I ask her about Canada,

05:27.015 --> 05:29.202
she kind of clams up.

05:29.216 --> 05:31.060
She's  a pretty private person.

05:31.075 --> 05:33.943
Except when she's
talking about...

05:33.958 --> 05:36.500
Oh, a friend of mine in Canada
got married way too young

05:36.606 --> 05:39.032
and it really turned
her off to marriage.

05:39.047 --> 05:40.733
What do you think of
this wedding cake?

05:40.748 --> 05:42.240
Oh, I like it.

05:42.255 --> 05:43.762
Hey, you remember that
friend of mine in Canada

05:43.796 --> 05:45.403
who got married way too young?

05:45.416 --> 05:48.740
Her wedding cake was a Mrs. Fields'
giant cookie.

05:50.018 --> 05:51.323
No.

05:53.546 --> 05:56.233
My friend in Canada who
got married way too young,

05:56.246 --> 05:58.610
they had to do their vows twice,
once in French.

05:58.628 --> 06:00.200
They speak French there, too?

06:00.213 --> 06:02.191
God, that place is a mess.

06:03.207 --> 06:06.193
So you don't think there's
any "friend" from Canada?

06:06.209 --> 06:07.502
Oh, I'm sure there is.

06:07.519 --> 06:10.211
Just like I have a "friend" who
wet his bed till he was ten.

06:10.225 --> 06:11.923
Use your brain, Ted.

06:14.746 --> 06:16.732
Guys, there's no way
Robin is married.

06:16.745 --> 06:18.481
It's ludicrous to
even suggest it.

06:18.497 --> 06:20.740
- Thank you, Barney.
- 'Cause it's porn.

06:20.756 --> 06:22.411
I need another beer.

06:22.755 --> 06:25.711
Robin was not in porn.
I bet you anything that she's married.

06:25.725 --> 06:27.311
$20,000 says it's porn.

06:27.326 --> 06:28.653
I don't have $20,000.

06:28.667 --> 06:30.551
Well, then what do you have?

06:31.248 --> 06:33.120
- Well...
- No.

06:33.875 --> 06:36.573
I've got it.
The ultimate wager--

06:36.586 --> 06:37.862
slap bet.

06:37.876 --> 06:40.100
Oh, slap bet.
We used to do those when I was a kid.

06:40.117 --> 06:41.420
What the hell's a slap bet?

06:41.435 --> 06:43.413
Whoever is right gets to slap
the other person in the face

06:43.447 --> 06:45.701
as hard as they possibly can--
but no rings.

06:45.718 --> 06:48.391
Are you really going to do that?
That's so immature.

06:48.407 --> 06:51.112
- You can be Slap Bet Commissioner.
- Ooh, I love it. What are my powers?

06:51.148 --> 06:54.183
Um, if a problem arises and we
need a ruling, that's your job.

06:54.195 --> 06:55.973
But you have to be unbiased

06:55.985 --> 06:59.232
and put the integrity of
slap bet above all else.

06:59.247 --> 07:01.973
This is an honor you will
take with you to your grave.

07:01.985 --> 07:03.713
On your tombstone,
it will read,

07:03.726 --> 07:07.050
"Lily Aldrin, caring wife,
loving friend,

07:07.066 --> 07:09.040
Slap Bet Commissioner."

07:09.616 --> 07:13.893
And your tombstone will read "Got
slapped by Marshall, so hard he died."

07:15.396 --> 07:19.410
Okay. What if I just ask Robin
point blank if she has a husband?

07:19.425 --> 07:21.521
You said you would
respect her privacy,

07:21.538 --> 07:23.710
so maybe you should
just drop it.

07:23.896 --> 07:25.592
Yeah, you're right.

07:27.498 --> 07:28.930
Husband.

07:30.496 --> 07:32.471
There's no "P" in husband.

07:32.486 --> 07:35.471
Wow, you seem to know
a lot about husbands.

07:35.925 --> 07:38.012
Fine. I'll take it back.

07:38.297 --> 07:41.072
Oh, hey, since you mentioned husbands,
this is great, you're going to love this.

07:41.105 --> 07:43.703
Marshall, you know Marshall.
He thinks that the reason

07:43.716 --> 07:45.240
you didn't want to go to
the mall the other day

07:45.275 --> 07:49.370
