something like that to myself?

09:20.527 --> 09:21.871
And you begged me to tell you.

09:21.888 --> 09:23.330
No, I didn't.

09:23.778 --> 09:26.380
Please tell us. Just tell us.
I'm begging you.

09:26.395 --> 09:28.593
Tell us. Tell us. Tell us.
Please please please--

09:28.607 --> 09:31.090
Fine. Robin's married.

09:33.015 --> 09:35.181
Yeah, well,
you still shouldn't have told us.

09:35.196 --> 09:37.102
I mean,
what kind of boyfriend are you?

09:37.117 --> 09:39.122
See that's just it,
I'm not the boyfriend.

09:39.136 --> 09:40.543
I'm the mistress.

09:40.555 --> 09:41.993
No, not the mistress.

09:42.006 --> 09:43.490
The mastress.

09:43.506 --> 09:45.040
The master.
What do you call it?

09:45.057 --> 09:47.150
Uh, pretty sure we're
going to call it mistress.

09:48.155 --> 09:51.351
What am I going to do?
My girlfriend's married.

09:51.365 --> 09:52.903
Do I ask her to get a divorce?

09:52.918 --> 09:56.081
Ted, even if she is married,
it's a Canadian marriage.

09:56.098 --> 09:58.151
It's like their money,
or their army.

09:58.166 --> 10:00.210
Nobody takes it seriously.

10:00.225 --> 10:01.411
It's serious to me.

10:01.426 --> 10:03.322
You know what, in some countries,
if you been separated

10:03.357 --> 10:06.073
for longer than five years,
technically, you're no longer married.

10:06.085 --> 10:08.632
I can check it out at the
law library at school.

10:10.758 --> 10:13.560
I can see my hand
print on your face.

10:13.738 --> 10:16.291
Don't get too cocky, Slappy.

10:16.306 --> 10:19.363
I just got a shipment of porn
from Canada I have to go through.

10:19.376 --> 10:21.372
I won the bet.
Why are you still searching?

10:21.387 --> 10:23.181
Just because you were right
doesn't mean I'm wrong.

10:23.215 --> 10:26.542
Oh, right, like you need 
an excuse to watch porn.

10:26.587 --> 10:28.791
Canadian porn.

10:28.808 --> 10:31.340
Trust me when I tell you their
universal health care system

10:31.355 --> 10:33.792
