10:44.617 --> 10:46.352
- Hey.
- Hey.

10:46.608 --> 10:48.551
Listen, dude,
I got to talk to you,

10:48.568 --> 10:51.722
but you got to promise me
that you won't tell Barney.

10:51.738 --> 10:54.241
Fine, I won't tell Barney.
What is it?

10:55.516 --> 10:58.001
- Robin's not married.
- What?

10:58.017 --> 10:59.500
Why would she tell me she was?

10:59.518 --> 11:01.660
I don't know, but I cross-
checked every record in Canada.

11:01.696 --> 11:03.552
There's no record of
her ever being married.

11:03.567 --> 11:04.692
There must be some mistake.

11:04.705 --> 11:06.510
I promise you.
She's not married.

11:06.527 --> 11:08.872
She's not great at
parking legally either.

11:09.318 --> 11:12.740
So she lied to me?
W--What am I going to do?

11:12.757 --> 11:15.780
I-I can't confront her,
'cause then she'll know I told you.

11:16.416 --> 11:18.072
You got to lawyer her. 

11:18.085 --> 11:20.631
You got to ask her a bunch of questions,
try to trip her up,

11:20.647 --> 11:22.223
maybe make her feel guilty,
whatever it takes

11:22.258 --> 11:24.063
to get a confession out of her.

11:25.227 --> 11:27.402
Thanks for telling
me your secret.

11:27.416 --> 11:29.871
It means so much to me,
that you could be so--

11:29.886 --> 11:31.723
God, what's the word
I'm looking for?

11:31.808 --> 11:32.881
Honest.

11:32.898 --> 11:34.682
Mm, thanks, Ted.

11:34.697 --> 11:36.832
Yeah.  You know what's probably
the best part about your honesty?

11:36.865 --> 11:38.703
How truthful it is.

11:39.037 --> 11:40.821
I say we just move on.

11:41.867 --> 11:43.973
Well, for me to get total
closure on this whole

11:43.988 --> 11:46.192
"my girlfriend has
a husband" thing,

11:46.297 --> 11:47.951
