little bit more information,

11:47.988 --> 11:49.892
like what month did
you get married?

11:49.905 --> 11:51.740
June. We had a June wedding.

11:51.758 --> 11:54.100
Ah, Canada in June.

11:54.117 --> 11:55.931
That's the dream.

11:56.876 --> 11:58.772
Sit-down or buffet?

11:59.418 --> 12:02.551
Well, it's...
weird that you don't remember.

12:02.567 --> 12:04.731
No, I just didn't
know how to answer

12:04.746 --> 12:07.691
because we did butlered hors
d'oeuvres in the atrium,

12:07.707 --> 12:10.733
but the actual dinner was
a buffet in the Food Court

12:10.747 --> 12:14.132
