12:28.315 --> 12:31.851
'cause I just love that
smooth alto sound.

12:31.865 --> 12:33.540
- How many bridesmaids?
- Seven.

12:33.557 --> 12:34.861
- Flowers?
- Azaleas.

12:34.878 --> 12:37.160
- Color scheme?
- Dusty rose and sienna.

12:37.175 --> 12:38.961
Husband's name.

12:41.415 --> 12:43.203
- You were never married!
- Yes, I was.

12:43.216 --> 12:45.142
- No, you weren't.
- How do you know?

12:45.158 --> 12:46.543
I looked it up at the library.

12:46.555 --> 12:50.133
- What library?
- The one on Fifth.

12:50.148 --> 12:52.051
- When did you go?
- Today at lunch,

12:52.068 --> 12:54.100
and I had an apple brie
panini with potato salad...

12:54.116 --> 12:56.343
I'm not questioning
the lunch part, Ted.

